What Happens After Decision
Auto Close
Ticket gets:
Summary
Evidence
Reasoning
Closure notes
Then closes automatically.
Assign to Team
AAMS:
Changes priority
Routes to correct queue
Sends notification email
Adds investigation notes
Human Approval
For P1/P2/P3:
AAMS NEVER closes directly.
Instead:
AAMS recommendation
↓
Team Lead review
↓
Approve / Reject
↓
Close
Safety control built in.
